Descriptions


kz_bricks
Original map by FOF
contains 3 courses: kz_bricks, bhop_genesis and bhop_velocity

kz_cavewell
Original map by Kangaroo
contains 2 courses: kz_cavewell and bhop_kz_rocks
Note for server owners, add a glitch zone for the bhop course that covers the KZ track (So you can't use the KZ course to complete the bhop course)

kz_cityswingers
Original map by Kaos_nyrb and SoUlFaThEr
contains 2 courses: kz_antenna and surf_building
Note for servers owners, if using Shavit's timer the end zone is already placed.

kz_clocktower
Original map by DaTrippinHobbit, Kangaroo and SoUlFaThEr
contains 2 courses: kz_clocktower and bhop_minilongjumprace


kz_cookbook
Original map author unknown
contains 2 courses: kz_cookbook_hard and kz_bridge
notes: Only ported the hard course as having two courses would be impossible in multiplayer without making a complicated filter system and moved the end of kz_cookbook to skip the maze, didn't feel like a crouch hold maze after a 10+ minute kz_course was very fun or enjoyable, it's not removed and you can still get there with noclip.

bhop_cartooncastle_kzmod
Original map by solid
contains 1 course: bhop_cartooncastle
notes: This map already exists on CSS but it's an older/beta version, this is a longer and more updated version with the optional ability to enable the music via this stripper (https://0x0.st/obhb.txt)
